838,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T12:54:09.000Z","msg":"我思故我在"},{"pid":"b6e95999c2c72d3e23e88a21f79f3984593e6803","tid":190838,"uid":96129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:09:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我思故我在</blockquote><br />\n我思故我在好似唔係咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n好似係笛卡苗對一切都抱有懷疑覺得世界上好多事物都不能證實而諗諗下佢諗到唯一證實到嘅就係自己存在緊嘅事實因為佢思考緊。<br />\n<br />\n（利申：門外漢9 up)<br />\n召喚巴打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5164f4f2ae719e18b0d9911ec66760c7d467af5e","tid":190838,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:11:32.000Z","msg":"因為生命無意義苦悶，<br />\n人先會開始反思自己生命<br />\n即係話想反抗但又唔敢，<br />\n－－其實就係咁簡單。"},{"pid":"b9fa7cdd1fbf343e918f97f0490cdb2cc3c565ad","tid":190838,"uid":96129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:13:34.000Z","msg":"人生存到底有無意義？係自己賦予還是外力賦予？人類咁樣一直繁殖下一代，到底有無咩集體嘅意義？"},{"pid":"322d07cf7c43baf3a870b76443af740ef949db39","tid":190838,"uid":84021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T18:24:59.000Z","msg":"諗唔透。哲學撚朋友介紹其中一個方向，睇你既工具價值、終極價值係咩，幫幫地到我。快樂咪得囉？"},{"pid":"d1d79d7d023f0637b0e800240acafb84d8a5f3e5","tid":190838,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T18:31:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e90c1afb76c3c16bc853a617dc87a372024a79b","tid":190838,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T18:52:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗唔透。哲學撚朋友介紹其中一個方向，睇你既工具價值、終極價值係咩，幫幫地到我。快樂咪得囉？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />試下投靠 Hedonism"},{"pid":"139d1ce9021d9d536cbeac0548ce86a903e6e458","tid":190838,"uid":16650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T19:04:28.000Z","msg":"存在於E個社會上既人既迷網，可以用馬思洛金字塔解釋"},{"pid":"436951516cbe06da194d1bdd30a0d490276e82e1","tid":190838,"uid":634